data.description: Dive into Dundee with this charming home! Step inside to discover the timeless charm of original hardwood floors and trim, coupled with modern luxury in a beautifully renovated bathroom. With an unfinished upstairs, there's ample opportunity to add space, value, and your personal touch to the home. The stainless steel fridge and dishwasher, along with the one-year-old washer and dryer, are all included for your convenience. Nestled in a coveted Dundee location, just minutes from UNMC and a straight 10-minute shot downtown, this property is lucrative opportunity in an area of high demand. PRE-Inspected!
